From: bibleadmin <admin@bibleclub.fun>
Date: Sun, 29 Mar 2026 21:30:08 -0700
Subject: [PATCH 2/2] Add Blue AI feed, conversation view, and card
 interactions

- Blue AI feed screen with BlueCard components showing video analysis
- BlueCardDetailScreen with message thread, audio playback states, timestamps
- BlueCard: blurry video thumbnail, 4-line summary, View Report, Share
- Island updates for Blue-specific actions
- VideoZoom: directVideoUrl param for Blue card video playback
- Mock data for Blue cards with real video URLs

Co-Authored-By: Claude Opus 4.6 <noreply@anthropic.com>
